  "text": "The nurse in the health care centres had on average 13 appointments with the intervention women. The intervention women had no instruction on self glucose monitoring before GDM was diagnosed. The nutritionist gave dietary advice tailored to each subject individually six times. The three-factor eating questionnaire was used in the beginning of pregnancy and at weeks 36-40 [CITATION_1] .",
